\mt1 GALESIA
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Wun Pol wun. Wan pas wunay…® p…®l…®wukna. Wun Aposel wun. Ndu nyan wun kat ana wand…® aposel t…®wangat. God k…®ta nyan kat wan nyaang…®t ana kwind…® wun kat wand…® maa aposel t…®wangat. Jisas Kraistno n…®na nyaek Godno mb…®tnai wamb…®t maa aposel t…®gowun. Tat God wand…® mala Jisas Kraist kiyalaa laatnd…®.
\v 2 Wunogwinala l…®a k…®ta mbaapma n…®mba ngwuk kat apma nandinya wal…®gandi. Ngwutna kava Galesia wal…®nja kavamba l…®ga ngepma ngepmamba God kat yelav…®pmak yisolaa l…®ga n…®mba kat aywaa apma nandinya wal…®gan…®n.
\p 
\v 3 N…®na nyaek Godno n…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraistno ngwuk kat apma vat awagapma kwimbangat wowun. Apma maawutno t…®ngwangat apma vat kwimbangat wowun.
\v 4 Kraist yalaa nd…®na mbang…® n…®n kat t…®ga avla kwo kwind…®. Mbambala l…®ga kavle vat tat n…®n kat ngilaa l…®nd…®. Wungi kavel vak kat njalapmat Krasit yand…®. N…®na nyaek God wand…® mala yand…®.
\v 5 God n…®n kat apma vat yind…®. Ngi kat t…®ga nj…®mbla nj…®mbla nd…®na s…® kwusogiyan…®n. Apma vatna.
\s1 WAN APMA NYAANG∆óT K∆óTGA M∆óNA L∆óGAND∆ó
\p 
\v 6 Wal…®ngwa vak wutaa ng…®pali waa laakwun. S…®vla ana l…® ngwuk kat kwagalawa. Kwagalawun maa kwiyatapman Kraistna apma nyaang…®k kat kwagalalaa mand…®t nyaang…®t kwutaa l…®gangwuk. God ngwuk kat wuna lak yagwa ngwula waa wand…®. Ngwuk nd…® kat manda kat kwagalavat t…®gangwuk.
\v 7 Wan apma nyaang…®t n…®ma sakwat kai. K…®ta l…®gand…®. Nat apma nyaang…®t ana l…®gand…®. Nat n…®mba ngwutna lak yandi. Kraistna apma nyaang…®k kat kai walaa nat mand…®t nyaang…®t mbut…®ndi. Mand…®t nyaang…®t ngambuga kavle vak yelav…®kngwangat ngwuk kat kwil…®gandi.
\v 8-9 Ke wula wan nyaang…®t. Ensel k…®ta ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga ngaga yalaa ngwuk kat mbut…®na apma nyaang…®k kat kai walaa mand…®t nyaang…®t kwindeyan ke wuka. Wan ensel ya v…®t…®ga kavat yigiyand…®. N…®no n…®mbun ngwuk kat mbut…®na apma nyaang…®k kat kai walaa mand…®t nyaang…®t kwineyan ya v…®t…®ga kavat yigiyan…®n.
\p 
\v 10 Wan nyaang…®t tat tamba wowun. Nat njamba wavat yigowun. N…®namba wutaa kwutaa l…®ngwa nyaang…®k kat k…®ta nyan kai walaa mand…®t nyaang…®t mbutndeyan ana nglaat…®. Wan nyan ya v…®t…®ga kavat yigiyand…®.
\s1 POL APOSEL T∆óNDA VAK
\p 
\v 11 K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba k…®ta nyaang…®t ngwuk kat mbupmat t…®gowun. Ngwuk kat mbukwa apma nyaang…®t ndu nyan waa nyaang…®t ana nd…®.
\v 12 K…®ta nyananamba wungi vat nyaang…®t ana wutwun. K…®ta nyan wungi vat nyaang…®t wun kat ana mbutnd…®. Jisas Kraist nd…® nd…®nay…® wun kat wan nyaang…®t mbukna.
\p 
\v 13 Tamba la nj…®mbla Juda yeta vak vla yetuwa nj…®mbla yet…®luwa vak kat tamba wukngwuk. God yagwa wanda n…®mba ndi kat n…®ma vat yil…®wun. Godna mbaapma n…®mba kat s…®vat t…®l…®wun. Tamba wukngwuk.
\v 14 Wuna k…®ta l…®v…® n…®mba kat Judana pavu kat kwulakwun. N…®na ngwatna vak n…®mbun ndi kat kwulakwun.
\p 
\v 15 God yetuwa vapmba yet…®wangat kai wand…®. Apma vapmba yet…®wangat God wand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga name wun kat kwutapman t…®la nj…®mbla God wun kat v…®ga l…®nd…®. Wun kat v…®laa m…®n wuna lak yaigam…®n nd…®na maawupmba God wand…®.
\v 16 Wun tamba n…®ma nyan t…®wun mala God nd…®na maawupmba wun kat nd…®na nyan Jisas kat v…®s…®mongwind…® waa v…®wun. God wun kat wand…®. Wuna apma nyaang…®t Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba kat yiga ambuk waa wand…®. Nd…®na nyaang…®t wutaa nat n…®mba kat ana wagalawun.
\v 17 Jerusalemat ana yiwun aposel kat wagalavat. Jerusalemba l…®ga n…®mba tat aposelat t…®ndi. Wun ng…®ni aposel t…®gowun. God waa nyaang…®t wutaa nat kavat Arebia wal…®nja kavat yiwun. Wan kava kwagalalaa Damaskas wal…®nja ngepmat yiwun.
\p 
\v 18 Naambi kuvut yind…® maa Pita kat wagalavat Jerusalemat yiwun. Ndinonala sande v…®l…®l…®k t…®wun.
\v 19 Nat n…®ma sakwat aposel kat ana v…®wun. Aposel v…®l…®l…®k mb…®k kat m…®na v…®wun. Pitogwi Jems kat m…®na v…®wun. Jems Jisasna yakwa nyana.
\v 20 Ngwuk kat p…®l…®wukwa nyaang…®t woseka ana wowun. Apma nyaang…®tna. God wun kat v…®ga l…®gand…®. Woseka ana wowun nd…® v…®ga l…®gand…®.
\p 
\v 21 Jerusalem kwagalalaa Siria wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pmamba l…®ga ngepma ngepmat Silisia wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pmamba l…®ga ngepma ngepmat yi ya l…®wun.
\v 22 Yi ya yet…®wa nj…®mbla Judiamba l…®ga Kraistna mbaapma n…®mba wuna m…®ndama ana v…®ga l…®ndi. Wuna s…® ana wuka l…®ndi. Kwutuwa nj…®vwa nat n…®mba v…®laa ndi kat yiga mbutndi. Mbutndi maa wutndi.
\v 23 Waa n…®mb…® wun kat wupma wandi. An nyan Pol tat n…®n kat n…®ma vat yil…®nd…®. Pol vat yiga ndi kat s…®ga viya yet…®nda n…®mba mbuta apma nyaang…®t nd…® yiga mbut…®gand…® waa wal…®ndi.
\v 24 Wan nyaang…®t wutaa Judiamba l…®ga n…®mba wandi. God Pol kat apma vat yind…®. God apma nyana waa wandi.
\c 2
\s1 POLAGWI NAT APOSELO
\p 
\v 1 T…®ga l…®ga nd…®mwe tamba v…®l…®i kiyeli aynat yind…® maa wunagwi Banabaso Jerusalemat yili. K…®ta nyan Taitas nd…® kat wowun mala angwinala k…®ta vat yind…®.
\v 2 God wun kat wand…®, wun yiwun. Jerusalemba la Jisasna mbaapmamba la n…®ma n…®mbanala wun yiga yisolaa l…®wun. Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba kat mbutuwa apma nyaang…®t ndi kat mbut…®wun. Jerusalema la n…®ma sakwat kwo n…®mba kat ana mbut…®wun wan nj…®mbla. N…®ma n…®mba kat m…®na mbut…®wun. Pol mbuta nyaang…®t wutaa ng…®ni kavle nyaang…®tna waa wana wal…®ngweya waa ndi kat mbut…®wun. Pol mbuta nyaang…®t kavle nyaang…®tna waa n…®ma wanjeyan wunai kwutaa nj…®vwa kwo vatnat t…®giyand…®. Kwukweya nj…®vwa n…®mbun kwo vatna t…®giyand…®.
\v 3-5 Nat n…®mba wan yisolaa l…®na kava yalaa n…®n kat woseka wandi. N…®no ngwutnogwinala k…®ta mbaapma n…®mba n…®n waa woseka wandi. N…®na mbaapma n…®mba ana ndi. N…®n Kraist Jisasna mbaapma wuleilaa Juda yeta vak vla ana yet…®n…®n. Kwagalalaa vak kat wan n…®mba s…®ga naguga v…®vat yandi. N…®n kat yalaa Judana yeta vapmba yet…®n…®ngat wandi. Wunagwinala yeta nyan Taitas nd…® Juda ana nd…®. Nd…® Grikna. Wan nyan kat Judana mbang…® p…®t…®nja vak vla nd…®na mbang…® wan woseka wala n…®mba p…®pmak wandi. Ndi kat kai waa kwulakn…®n. Nd…®na mbang…® ana p…®tndi. Tak ngwutnogwinala yet…®na nj…®mbla ngwuk kat Juda yeta vak vla yet…® ngwula waa ana wan…®n. Jerusalemba l…®ga wan wana apma nyaang…®t kat kal…®pmak kat kai wan…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga ndi kat kai wan…®n.
\p 
\v 6 Wan Jerusalemba la nat n…®mba ndina nat n…®mba kat n…®mba n…®mba t…®nja vak v…®ga l…®ndi. N…®ma n…®mba t…®nja vak wun ana v…®ga l…®gowun. N…®ma n…®mba t…®nja vak God ana v…®ga l…®gand…®. Nd…® ndina maawut m…®na v…®ga l…®gand…®. Wan wanja n…®mba n…®mba wuna nyaang…®k kat kal…®pmak ana ngambundi.
\v 7 Wan Jerusalemba la nat n…®mba ndina nat n…®mba kat n…®ma n…®mba t…®nja vak v…®ga l…®ndi. N…®ma n…®mba t…®nja vak wun ana v…®ga l…®gowun. N…®ma n…®mba t…®nja vak God ana v…®ga l…®gand…®. Nd…® ndina maawut m…®na v…®ga l…®gand…®. Wan wanja n…®ma n…®mba wuna nyaang…®k kat kal…®pmak ana ngambundi.
\v 8 God Pita kat kwondu kwind…® maa Juda kat aposelna nj…®vwa kwuka waa apma nyaang…®t Pita mbut…®nd…®. Wuno n…®mbun. God wun kat kwondu kwind…® maa Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba kat aposelna nj…®vwa kwuka waa apma nyaang…®t wun mbut…®wun.
\v 9 Kuvuk n…®mba Pita, Jems, jon ndi kat njambwi n…®mba ndi wandi. God wun kat n…®ma nj…®vwa kwind…® waa ndi kuvut n…®mba v…®ga l…®ndi. Ngi kat t…®ga wunogwi Banabas kat angat taamba kwutndi. K…®mb…®k kwutaa wandi. Pologwi banabaso wan Godna apma nyaang…®t Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba kat mbukiyamb…®t. N…®n wan apma nyaang…®t Juda kat mbukiyan…®n waa wandi.
\v 10 Wun kat k…®ta nyaang…®t m…®na mbutndi. N…®nogwinala l…®ga kwanda kwanda lapman wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa yet…®wun. Ndi kat kwunapmak n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®wun.
\s1 ANTIOKMBA POL PITA KAT KAI WAND∆ó
\p 
\v 11 Wun Antiok wal…®nja ngepmamba l…®wun. Pita yand…®. Kapmba vas…®gla laataa nd…® kat kai wowun. Nd…® kavle vat yind…® maa nd…® kat kai wawa vat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba wutndi.
\v 12 Pita ya kavle vat k…®ngiyan. Tak Pita Antiok yalaa Juda ana ndi Jisasna mbaapma n…®mbonala Pita k…®tamba nao k…®ga l…®nd…®. Jems wand…® maa Jerusalemba la ndi Juda Jerusalem kwagalalaa Antiokat yandi. Yandi mala Pita Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba kat kwagaland…®. Wan yaa Juda wupma yelav…®tndi. Juda ana ndi yet…®na vapmba ndina mbang…® p…®tapman yijeyan ana glaatnd…® waa yelav…®tndi. Pita Juda waiga vak kat wutaa vaaka Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba kat kwagaland…®.
\v 13 Nat Jisasna mbaapmamba la Juda Pita kwagala la yet…®nda kavle vapmba yet…®ndi. Banabas nd…®no wupma yivat yelav…®tnd…®.
\v 14 Ndi Kraistna apma nyaang…®pmba ana yet…®ndi. Ngi kat t…®ga yet…®nja kavle vak kat v…®laa ndi kat kai wowun. Pita kat ndina m…®ndama samb…®mba wowun. M…®n Juda m…®n. M…®n tat Juda ana ndi nat n…®mbonala t…®ga nao k…®ga l…®m…®n. Juda yeta vak ana nd…®. M…®n Juda yeta vak kat kai walaa yet…®m…®n. Mbambala yaa Juda yet…®na vapmba Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba kat yet…®giyandi waa wandi. M…®n manda kat ndina kwundi wutaa ndina lak yim…®n waa wowun Pita kat.
\s1 NDINYANGU AYWAA GOD NDI KAT K∆óTA VAPMBA KWUNAT∆óGAND∆ó
\p 
\v 15 N…®n kat name kwut…® mala Judana mbaapma t…®gan…®n. Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba ana n…®n.
\v 16 N…®n k…®ta vak kat v…®ga l…®gan…®n. K…®ta nyan Juda yeta vapmba yet…®ndeyan God nd…® kat m…®n apma nyan m…®n waa ana waigand…®. K…®ta nyan Jisas Kraist kwuta nj…®vwa kat wuna lak yaand…® wandeyan God nd…® kat m…®n apma nyan m…®n waa waigand…®. Wanja nyaang…®t n…®no tamba wan…®n. N…®n Juda n…®mbun wan vapmba waneyan God n…®n kat apma n…®mba ngwuk waa waigand…®. K…®ta nyan Kraist kwuta nj…®vwa kat kwagalalaa Judana lomba yet…®ndeyan God nd…® kat apma nyan m…®n waa ana waigand…®.
\v 17 N…®n Kraist kwuta nj…®vwa kat n…®na lak yaand…® waa wan…®n. N…®n wupma waga yelav…®t…®gan…®n. K…®ta nyan Judana lomba yet…®lapman wuna lak yaand…® wandeyan God nd…® kat m…®n apma nyan m…®n waigand…® waa yelav…®t…®gan…®n. Judana lomba yet…®lapman yeineyan Juda ndi n…®n kat v…®laa waigandi. Ngwuk kavle vak yet…®l…®gangwuk waa waigandi. God n…®n kat v…®laa wupma ana waigand…®. Wungi kat t…®ga Kraistna vapmba yet…®ndeyan kavle vak ana yet…®giyan…®n.
\v 18 Nat n…®mba kat Juda yeta vapmba yet…® ngwula waneyan wan kavle vatna. Tak ngwuk kat mand…®t nyaang…®t wan…®n. Tak kupma wan…®n. Juda yeta la vapmba yet…®l…®na vak kat v…®laa God n…®n kat apma vatna waa ana waigand…® waa tat ngwuk kat wan…®n. Tat ngwuk kat mbut…®na apma nyaang…®t twagalalaa ng…®ni mand…®t nyaang…®pmba ngwuk kat waneyan waa kavle vatna.
\v 19 Wun Juda yeta lomba ana yet…®l…®gowun. Ana al…®ps…®ga yet…®l…®gowun. Wuna tamba yelav…®ka yetuwa kavle maawut tamba kiyand…®. Wun kiya nyan vla l…®gowun. Anda vapmba Juda yeta lomba yet…®giyowun. Ana al…®ps…®ga yet…®giyowun. Wun kat God waa nyaang…®pmba al…®ps…®ga yet…®l…®gowun.
\v 20 Kraist diwai krosmba kiya vla wuna tamba yelav…®ka yetuwa kavle maawut kiyand…®. Wunai yelav…®ka yet…®ga vapmba ana yet…®l…®gowun. Kraist waa nyaang…®tmba yet…®l…®gowun. Nd…® wuna maawupmba l…®ga yet…®weya vak kat wun kat mbut…®gand…®. Godna nyan wun kat yinda vak kat yelav…®ka yet…®l…®gowun. Wun kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®nd…®. Wun kat t…®ga kiyand…®.
\v 21 God n…®n kat awagapma kwunat…®nda vak kat ana kai waigowun. Lomba yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat m…®na God apma n…®mba ngwuk waa wandeyan Kraist manda kat n…®n kat t…®ga kiyand…®. God wupma ana wal…®gand…®.
\c 3
\s1 GOD N∆óN KAT APMA N∆óMBA NGWUK WAA WAIGAA VAT
\p 
\v 1 Ngwuk Galesiamba l…®ga manda kat tungwengwan yiga yelav…®t…®gangwuk. Kanda ngwutnamaawut kavle ya. Jisas Kraist kiwai krosmba kiya vak ngwuk kat tamba mbukwun maa wukngwuk. Kiyanda vak va n…®mba bla tamba l…®gwuk.
\v 2 Lomba yet…®ngwa vak kat v…®laa God nd…®na waagan ngwuk kat kwind…®? E? Kai luwa. Wan apma nyaang…®t wutaa ngwutna maawupmba kwutaa l…®ngwa vak v…®laa God nd…®na waagan ngwuk kat kwind…®.
\v 3 Manda kat tungwengwan yiga wan vak kwagalal…®gangwuk. Tak God nd…®na waagan ngwuk kat awagapma kwind…®. Wan vak kwagalalaa mbambala yelav…®t…®gangwuk. N…®na apma nj…®vwamba God kat kwunakiyan…®n waa yelav…®t…®gangwuk. Wupma ke yelav…®ka.
\v 4 God ngwuk kat tat ya vak kat ngwutna maawut t…®v…®l…®gand…®? Wun ngwutna maawut ana t…®v…®l…®gand…® waa yelav…®t…®gowun.
\v 5 Manda kat God nd…®na waagan njwutna lak kwind…®. Manda kat ngwuk kat God n…®ma nj…®vwa kwutnd…®. Lomba yet…®ngwa vak v…®laa kwutnd…®? Kai luwa. Wan apma nyaang…®t wutaa ngwutna maawupmba kwutaa l…®ngwa vak v…®laa kwutnd…®.
\p 
\v 6 Nd…®no Ebraham wupma. Tamba God waa nyaang…®tmba p…®l…®wutndi. Ebraham God waa nyaang…®t wutaa nd…®na mbang…® wiyo waavi taagand…®. Taaganda vak v…®laa God nd…® kat wand…®. M…®n apma nyan m…®n waa wand…® waa p…®l…®wutndi.
\v 7 K…®ta nda v…®ngwangat wowun. God kat ngwula mbang…® wiyo waavi taagnadeyan ngwuk Ebrahamna yelang…® n…®mba ngwuk.
\v 8 Tamba God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutaa n…®mba wan vak p…®l…®wutndi. Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba God kat ndina mbang…® wiyo waavi taaganda vak kat v…®laa God ndi kat apma n…®mba ngwuk waa wandeya vak kat tamba p…®l…®wutndi. Ngi kat t…®ga tat wan apma nyaang…®t Ebraham kat p…®l…®wutndi. God m…®n kat kwunatnda vak vla wan k…®pmana ngepma ngepmamba la n…®mba kat aywaa God ndi kat apma vat yigiyand…® waa tamba Ebraham kat p…®l…®wutndi.
\v 9 Ebraham God kat nd…®na mbang…® wiyo waavi taagand…® maa God nd…® kat apma vat yind…®. God kat nd…®na mbang…® wiyo waavi taaganda vla n…®na mbang…® wupma wiyo waavi taagandeyan n…®no wupma n…®n kat god apma vat yigiyand…®.
\v 10 Apma vapmba lomba yet…®ma vak kat v…®laa God wun kat apma vat kwigiyand…® waa k…®ta nyan ytelav…®tndeyan nd…® kat miwa ay. Tamba God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wuta n…®mba p…®l…®wutndi. ‚ÄúK…®ta nyan lo waa nyaang…®pmba aywaa yet…®levilaa‚Äù waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi.
\v 11 K…®ta vak v…®laa l…®ga maawupmba yelav…®tn…®n. Lomba yet…®l…®ngwa vak kat vl…®aa God ngwuk kat apma n…®mba ngwuk waa ana waigand…®. Tamba God waa nyaang…®tmba p…®l…®wutndi. K…®ta nyan God kat nd…®na mbang…® wiyo waavi taagdndeyan God nd…® kat kwunatnd…® maa apma vat kwo l…®giyand…® waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi.
\v 12 Lomba yet…®ngwa vak Jisasna nj…®vwa wuna lak yaand…® waa waneya vat kapma kapma vat mb…®t. Lomba yet…®ngwa vat kapma vatna. Wan vak kat God waa nyaang…®tmba tamba p…®l…®wutndi. K…®ta nyan n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka sakat samat lona vak kwutaa l…®ndeyan nd…® apma vapmba kwo l…®ga t…®giyand…® waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi.
\p 
\v 13 Lomba yet…®na vak n…®n kat kavle vat yigiyand…®. Wan kavle vat Kraistna lak yind…® n…®n kat t…®ga wan kavle vak n…®n kat ana v…®ga l…®gand…®. Tamba wan vak Kraist yinda vak kat God waa nyaang…®tmba p…®l…®wutndi. K…®ta nyan m…®mba kaalajeyan wan nyan kai kavle vat aywaa nd…®na lak yind…® waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi.
\v 14 God n…®n kat apma vat yivat wand…®. Tak God Ebraham kat wand…®. Ndinyangu kat apma vat yigiyowun wand…®. God Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba kat apma vat yivat wand…® God. Ngi kat t…®ga God yelav…®tnd…®. Kraist Jisas kiyanda vak kat n…®n kat t…®ga kiyand…® waa yelav…®tnjeyan ndi kat wuna waagan kwigiyowun waa yelav…®tnd…® God.
\s1 TAMBA LA LO GOD WAA NYAANG∆óK KAT ANA KWULAKIYAND∆ó
\p 
\v 15 Wuna k…®tambaapma n…®mba ngwuk kat wupuseput mbupmat yigowun. Kan mbukwa wapuseput ngwula maawuk kat kwunakiyand…®. V…®l…®l…®k pal…® paak awat sowat tamba kwiga klamb…®t. Ng…®ni yaiga nat k…®ta nyan mb…®la paak kat ana kai waigand…®.
\v 16 Tamba Ebrahamgwi Godno paak awat sowat kwiga klamb…®t. Ebrahamogwi nd…®na yelang…®mba l…®giyaa nyano mb…®k kat God paak kwind…®. Wan paakmba l…®ga God waa nyaang…®t Ebrahamna yelag…®mba l…®giyaa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat ana wand…®. Nd…®na yelang…®mba l…®giyaa k…®ta nyan kat wand…®. Wan k…®ta nyan Kraist Jisasa.
\v 17 Wan nyaang…®k kat yelav…®k ngwula. Godnogwi ebrahamo paak tamba kwiga klamb…®t. Ndimwe 430 yind…® maa Moses kwiya lo wan tamba klamba paak kat ana kai wand…®. God tamba Ebraham kat waa nyaang…®k kat ana kwulatnd…®.
\v 18 Lomba yet…®nangat God n…®n kat kwivat wanda nda n…®n kat kwindeyan n…®n wupma waigan…®n. God waa nyaang…®tmba ana klan…®n. N…®n n…®na nj…®vwamba klan…®n waa waigan…®n. God wupma ana kwigiyand…®. M…®n kat apma vat yigiyowun waa Ebraham kat walaa God nd…® kat apma vat yind…®. Ebraham lomba yet…®nda vak kat vkilaa God ana kwind…®.
\p 
\v 19 Lo manda kat God Moses katkwind…®. Lona vat m…®nda vatna. Wan lona vak k…®ngiyan. Ndinyangu aywaa wan lo kat v…®laa yelav…®kiyandi. N…®n kavle savle yet…®n…®n waa yelav…®kiyandi. Kavle savle yt…®nja vak kat ndi kat s…®mogwivat God wan lo ng…®ni kwind…®. Ebrahamna yelang…®mba la k…®ta nyan Kraist yand…® maa lona nj…®vwa ng…®l…®nd…®. Wan lo God ensel kat kwind…®, Moses kat kwindi. Kwindi maa ndinyangu kat kwind…®. Wan nyan Moses n…®nd…®mba la nyana.
\v 20 God Ebraham kat paak kwinda nj…®mbla n…®nd…®mba la nyan ana l…®nd…®. God nd…® kapma l…®ga kwind…®.
\s1 LONA VAT
\p 
\v 21 Wan lo God waa nyaang…®k kat ana kal…®kiyand…®. Wan lo God waa nyaang…®t kapma kapma nj…®vwa vla l…®gamb…®t. Wan lo ndinyangu kat ana kwunat…®gand…®. Nd…®na nj…®vwa kapma nj…®vwa vla l…®gand…®. Lona nj…®vwa ndu nyan kat kwunat…®ga vla l…®ndeyan k…®ta nyan lomba yet…®ga nyan nd…® wan nyan kwo l…®giyand…®.
\v 22 God waa nyaang…®t tamba p…®l…®wutnja nyaang…®t kapma nyaang…®tna. Ndinyangu aywaa kavle savle yet…®l…®gandi. God waa lomba ana yet…®l…®gandi waa tamba God waa nyang…®tmba p…®l…®wutndi. Ngi kat t…®ga God ndinyangu kat wand…®. ngwuk Jisas Krasit kwuta nj…®vwa n…®na lak yaand…® wangweyan ngwuk kat apma vat kwo kwunakiyowun waa wand…® God.
\v 23 Tat lo n…®n kat ngilaa l…®nd…®. Mbambala ngilaa l…®nda vak ng…®l…®nd…®. Mbambala Jisas kwutaa nj…®vwa kat maawupmba yelav…®tneyan God n…®n kat kwo kwunakiyand…®.
\v 24 Tat lo n…®n kat v…®ga la nyan vla l…®nd…®. Jisas Kraistna mbaapma wuleinangat n…®n maawupmba l…®ga wand…®. N…®na maawupmba God waa nyaang…®t kwutaa l…®n…®n, God n…®n kat apma n…®mba ngwuk wand…®.
\v 25 Mbambala n…®na maawupmba God waa nyaang…®k kat kwutaa l…®gan…®n. N…®n kat v…®ga la lo ana v…®ga l…®gand…®.
\v 26 N…®n Kraist Jisas kwuta nj…®vwa kat v…®laa n…®n kat t…®ga kwutnd…® waa yelav…®t…®gan…®n. Maawupmba yelav…®tna vak kat v…®laa God ngwut wuna nyangu ngwuk wal…®gand…®.
\v 27 Kraistna yelang…® wuleil…®ga nyan nd…® Kraist yeta vak vla yet…®l…®ga nyana.
\v 28 Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba ndi k…®ta vapmba l…®ga n…®mba ndi. N…®n kapma kapma n…®mba n…®n waa ana waigan…®n. N…®n Juda n…®n ngwuk Juda ana ngwuk waa ana waigan…®n. N…®n nj…®vwa kwut…®ga n…®mba n…®n ngwuk kwo v…®ga la n…®mba ngwuk waa ana waigan…®n. N…®n ndu n…®n ngwuk taagwa ngwuk waa ana waigan…®n. Kraist Jisasonala n…®n k…®ta vapmba yet…®l…®gan…®n.
\v 29 Kraistna mbaapmamba l…®ngweyan ngwuk Ebrahamna nyangu ngwuk. God Ebraham kat kwivat wanda nda ngwulo ngwuk kat kwigiyand…®.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Tamba ngwuk kat wawa nyaang…®t nat samat ngambuvat wowun. K…®ta nyana mat nyan ng…®ni nd…®na nyaekna wowun. K…®ta nyana mat nyan ng…®ni nd…®na nyaekna kwanda kwanda klalaa v…®ga l…®giyand…®. Mbambala mat nyana. Ana v…®ga l…®gand…®. Ndi kwo nyan vla l…®gand…®.
\v 2 Mat nyan t…®ga yet…®nda vak nd…®na nyaek waa n…®mba nat n…®mba v…®ga l…®ndi nd…® kat. D…®na nyaek waa nj…®mbla yand…® maa nd…® kat v…®ga la n…®mba kwagalandi maa nd…® avla v…®ga l…®giyand…® nd…®na nda kat.
\v 3 N…®no wungi vat s…®g…®t. Tat mat nyan vla l…®n…®n. K…®pmana vat n…®n kat v…®ga l…®nd…®. N…®na maawut yigumba ana yelav…®ka l…®n…®n.
\v 4 God waa nandinya yand…® maa God nd…®na nyan n…®n kat kwind…®. K…®pmana taagwa ndi kat kwut…® maa l…®nd…®. Yalaa Juda yeta vapmba yet…®nd…®.
\v 5 Juda yeta vak nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat ngilaa l…®nd…®. Wungi vak kat njalapmat yand…®. Godna n…®mba t…®nangat yand…®.
\p 
\v 6 Ngwuk Godna n…®mba t…®ngwangat ngwuk kat s…®magavat God nd…®na waagan kwind…®. Godna waagan n…®na maawupmba l…®ga wal…®gand…®. God ngwula nyaekna waa n…®n kat wal…®gand…®.
\v 7 Mbambala ngwut kwo n…®mba ana ngwuk. Tamba Godna nyangu ngwuk. Ngwuk Godna nyangu kat kwindeya kwanda kwanda klalaa v…®ga l…®giyangwuk.
\s1 GALESIAMBA LA N∆óMBA KAT POL N∆óMA VAT YELAV∆óKA L∆óND∆ó
\p 
\v 8 Tamba ngwuk Godna m…®ndama v…®ga nd…®na s…® ana wuka l…®ngwuk. K…®pmana vapmba yet…®ngwuk.
\v 9 Mbambala Godna m…®ndama v…®ga nd…®na s…® wuka l…®gangwuk. God ngwuk kat v…®ga l…®gand…®. Ngwuk manda kat wan vak kwagalalaa k…®pmana vapmba nat njamba yet…®vak wal…®gangwuk. Manda kat wan vak kwagalalaa k…®pmana s…®vu njambiyana vapmba kwutaa yet…®vak wal…®gangwuk.
\v 10 Ngwuk nandinyana njambiya mbakna njambiya ndimwena njambiyana vapmba yet…®l…®gangwuk.
\v 11 Wan kavle vak yingwa vak kat v…®laa n…®ma vak yelav…®ka t…®gowun. Gwutnogwinala l…®ga ngambuwa vat kwo vatnat anagand…® ya.
\p 
\v 12 Ngwuk k…®ta mbaapma n…®mba Judana njambiya kat yelav…®kwa vat ngwutno yelav…®k ngwula. Wan njambiya kat ana yelav…®ka l…®gowun. Ngwulo tak ana yelav…®ka l…®ngwuk. Tat ngwuk kat mbukwa nj…®mbla wun kat ana kai wangwuk. Manda kat mbambala kai wal…®gangwuk.
\v 13 Tak ngwula ngepma yiga tuwa nj…®mbla wun kat yelogwen kwutnd…®, t…®wun. T…®ga l…®ga ngwuk kat wan apma nyaang…®t mbukwun.
\v 14 Ngwuk kat yelav…®ka l…®gowun. Wuna mbang…® v…®vak kat kai wal…®ngwuk. Wuna yelogwen wuna mbang…® kavle savle l…®nd…®. Ngwuk wun kat ana kai wangwuk. Wun kat yingwa vak ensel k…®ta kat yingwa vak vla yingwuk. Wun kat yingwa vak Jisas Kraist kat yingwa vak vla yingwuk.
\v 15 Ngwuk wun kat solat s…®l…®ngwuk. Mbambala manda kat mand…®t maawut yelav…®t…®gangwuk. Tak ngwuk wuna yelogwen kat kwunapmak kat t…®ngwuk. Ngwuk ngwutna m…®ni p…®ngwuga klalaa wuna lak kwivak kat t…®ngwuk wuna yelogwen kwunapmak. Mbambala manda kat mand…®t maawut yelav…®t…®gangwuk.
\v 16 Ngwuk kat savagu la nyaang…®tna mbukwa. Ngwuk wun kat kimbuk yiga l…®gangwuk?
\p 
\v 17 Wuna kwupmba ya n…®mba ngwuk kat n…®mba nj…®vwa kwut…®ndi. Apma mnaawut yelav…®ka ana kwut…®ndi. K…®mb…®k kwutaa vak kal…®pmat t…®l…®ndi. Wun kat kai walaa ndina vapmba wukwangat t…®l…®ndi.
\v 18 Ngwuk kat apma vat yivat nj…®vwa kwutnja vat apma vatna. Woviyaguga l…®gowun. Mbambala wunngwulogwinala ana l…®gowun. Nat n…®mba ngwuk kat kwunapmat yanjan apma vatna. Woviyaguga l…®gowun. Wan n…®mba ngwuk kat yaa n…®mba ngwuk kat kavle vat yivat yandi.
\v 19 Ngwuk wuna nyangu vla l…®gangwuk. Wun nyan t…®ga taagwa kang…®t waa l…®ga vla wupma l…®gowun ngwuk kat. Kraist yeta vak ngwula maawupmba l…®ndeyan kang…®t yila vak vla ng…®l…®giyand…®. Wunai kwukna n…®mba vla l…®giyangwuk.
\v 20 Ngwuk kat miwa yiga l…®gowun. Ngwutnai l…®ga ngepmat yivat t…®gowun. Ngwutna m…®ndama v…®ga wan nyaang…®t mbupmak kat wowun. Pasmba p…®l…®wukweya ana nglaatnd…®. Ngwuk kat n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®gowun.
\s1 HEGAOGWI SERANA WAPUSEPUT
\p 
\v 21 Ngwuk Judana lomba yet…®vak wal…®gangwuk. Ngwuk kat k…®tga nda kat wagalavat yigowun. Lona vak kat yelav…®ka yet…®gangwuk? E? Ana yelav…®t…®giyangwuk? Lona vak kat ngwuk kat mbupmat yigowun.
\v 22 Tamba Ebrahamna nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutndi. Ebraham taagwa v…®l…®l…®k klal…®nd…®. Nat taagwa nd…®na taagwat. Nst taagwa nd…®na ngayna nj…®vwa kwuta taagwat. Wumb…®t taagwa nyan k…®ta k…®ta kwupmb…®k.
\v 23 Nd…®na ngayna nj…®vwa kwuta taagwakat Ebraham nyan taagand…® maa kwut…®. nat taagwa God waa nyaang…®pmba Ebraham nyan taagand…®, kwut…®.
\v 24-25 God ndinyangu kat kwiya v…®l…®l…®k ndana aveyamb…® vla l…®ga taagwa mb…®t. Nat taagwana s…® Hega. God Moses kat lo kwiya nj…®mbla Moses Sainai wal…®nja nduwimba wokelaa kland…®. Sainai wal…®nja nduwi Hega wal…®nja taagwana k…®pma. Hegagwi l…®la nyanondi kat nat n…®mba v…®ga l…®ndi. Ndina maawupmba ana yet…®ndi. Wan lo klala n…®mbana angwa ngepma Jerusalema. Ndi Juda ndi. Wundi Juda ndi lona nj…®vwa kwut…®ga n…®mba ndi. Nat n…®mba Hegana nyangu kat v…®ga l…®nja vak vla lo Juda kat v…®ga l…®nd…®. Ndi ndina maawupmba ana yet…®ndi.
\v 26 N…®n Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba n…®n. Jerusalem n…®na angwa ngepma ana nd…®. n…®na angwa ngepma ny…®nangwupmba l…®gand…®. Lona nj…®vwa kwut…®ga n…®mba ana n…®n. Lo n…®n kat ana kwutaa v…®ga l…®gand…®.
\v 27 Tamba Aisaia God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnd…®.
\li1 Ny…®n taagwa ny…®n nyan kwutapman t…®nya vak kat
\li1 ny…®n ke k…®l…®mal…® yelav…®ka laga. Nyan kwutapman
\li1 t…®ga ny…®n solat s…®ga yet…®. Ng…®ni nyangu n…®ma
\li1 sakwat kwukiyany…®n. Nyan kwut…®ga taagwa kat
\li1 kwulakka nyan kwukiyany…®n
\p waa wand…® God waa tamba Aisaia p…®l…®wutnd…®.
\v 28 Wan God waa nyaang…®t Sera kat yand…® maa Aisak kat kwut…®. n…®no Godna mbaapma n…®mba Godna nyangu n…®n. God wand…® maa nd…®na nyangu vla l…®gangwuk. Aisak ta vla l…®ga n…®n.
\v 29 Hegana nyan nd…® kwo yand…®. Ebrahamo Hego mb…®lai kwuta njsvwamba yand…®. Serana nyan God waa nyaang…®pmba yand…®. Hegana nyan Serana nyan kat walea l…®nd…®. Wan vak vata t…®vwaligand…® wan walea l…®mba vat. Nat n…®mba ndi Judana vapmba yet…®nangat wal…®gandi. Ngi kat t…®ga n…®n kat walea l…®gandi. N…®n Godna waagan waa nyaang…®pmba yet…®ga n…®mba n…®n.
\li1 
\v 30 Tamba God Ebraham kat wanda nyaang…®t nd…® Moses
\li1 p…®l…®wutnd…®. M…®na ngayna nj…®vwa kwuta taagwa
\li1 l…®la nyano m…®na ngaykat kai wam…®n yigamb…®t.
\li1 Wan nyan m…®na kwanda kwanda nda ana klaigand…®.
\li1 Nat nyan Sera kwukna nyan nd…® m…®na kwanda
\li1 kwanda nda aywaa klaigand…®
\p waa wand…® God Ebraham kat waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…® Moses.
\v 31 Wuna k…®ta mbaapma n…®mba, n…®n Hegana nyangu vla ana l…®gan…®n. Juda yet…®l…®ga lo n…®n kat ana kwutaa v…®ga l…®gand…®. Serana nyangu vla l…®gan…®n.
\c 5
\s1 KWO L∆óNA VAPMBA KWO YET∆óGIYAN∆óN
\p 
\v 1 Lo n…®n kat ngilaa l…®ndangat Kraist njalapmat yand…®. Ngwuk wupma kwo l…®giyangwuk. Judana loat nat njamba wana wuleingweya.
\p 
\v 2 Wuna kwundi m…®na awuk. Wun Pol wun. Kan nyaang…®t ngwuk kat mbukowun. Juda mbang…® p…®t…®nja vapmba n…®na mbang…® p…®tneyan God n…®n kat apma n…®mba ngwuk waa waigand…® waa yelav…®kngweyan Kraist ngwuk kat kwuta nj…®vwa ngwukkat ana kwunakiyand…®.
\v 3 Ak wawa vak nat njamba ngwuk kat wowun. Juda mbang…® p…®t…®nja vla n…®na mbang…® p…®tneyan God n…®n kat apma n…®mba ngwuk waa waigand…® waa yelav…®kngweyan Judana lomba aywaa yet…®giyangwuk. Ndina lomba yet…®levilaa yingweyan kavle vat t…®giyangwuk.
\v 4 Judana lomba yet…®na vak God v…®laa ngwuk apma n…®mba ngwuk waa waigand…® waa yelav…®kngweyan ana glaatnd…®. Wupma yelav…®kngweyan Kraist ngwuk kat ana al…®ps…®ga kwunakiyand…®. God ngwuk kat ana al…®ps…®ga awagapma apma vat yigiyand…®.
\v 5 N…®n wupma ana yelav…®t…®gan…®n. Kraist ya vak n…®na lak yaand…® waa waneya nyaang…®t God wutaa n…®n kat awagapma apma vat yil…®ngad…® waa yelav…®t…®gan…®n. God nd…®na waagan n…®n kat kwind…® maa nat njamba apma vat yindeya vak kat kawiga l…®gan…®n.
\v 6 Kraist Jisasogwinala k…®ta vat t…®neyan mbang…® p…®tneya vat God ana v…®giyand…®. P…®tapman t…®neya vak God ana v…®giyand…®. Wan vak n…®ma vak ana nd…®. N…®ma vak k…®ngiyan. Kraist kwuta nj…®vwa kat n…®na mbang…® wiyo waavi taagavat t…®gand…®. Taagand…® maa nat n…®mba kat kwunaka woviyaguga l…®gan…®n. Wan n…®ma vatna.
\p 
\v 7 Tak ngwuk wan apma nyaang…®t wuta savagu yet…®ngwuk. Kanda wandi maa wan apma nyaang…®k kat kwagalagangwuk. Anda vatna butndi maa mand…®t vat yelav…®kngwa.
\v 8 Ngwuk kat mbutnja nyaang…®t Godna nyaang…®t ana nd…®. God ngwuk kat mand…®t nyaang…®tmba yagwa wand…®.
\v 9 Yis samat taaganja bret-nao n…®ma nglei yind…®. Nd…®no wupma. Wan kavle nyaang…®t mbut…®nja nyaang…®t ngwutna maawupmba wuleilaa n…®ma nglei vak kavle yind…®.
\v 10 Wupma yelav…®ka l…®gowun. Wan kavle vat kwagalagiyangwuk. N…®n njambwi nyanonala k…®ta vat t…®gan…®n. K…®ta mbaapmamba l…®gan…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga k…®ngi vat t…®nan wan kavle vat kwagalagiyangwuk waa yelav…®ka l…®gowun. Wan nyan ngwutna maawut kavle yil…®ga nyan kat God nd…® kat n…®ma vat yigiyand…®.
\p 
\v 11 K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba ngwuk Judana vapmba mbang…® ap…®k ngwula waa ana yiga but…®gowun. Ngi kat t…®ga wun kat Juda waleavat t…®gandi. Judana vapmba mbang…® ap…®k ngwula waa mbukweyan Juda wun kat ana waleavat t…®giyandi. Kraist kiyaa vak kat mbukwa nyaang…®k kat ana kai waigandi. Wan nyaang…®t mbang…® ap…®k ngwula waa ana mbut…®gowun.
\v 12 Wan n…®mba ngwuk kat mbang…® ap…®k ngwula waa n…®mba ngwuk kat kai waa kwagalanjangat wowun.
\p 
\v 13 K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba, lo ngwuk kat y…®ga l…®vak kat God kai wand…®. kwo l…®nangat wand…®. Wupma wana yelav…®kngweya. N…®n kwo l…®ga tamba maawupmba yet…®giyan…®n waa wana yelav…®kngweya. Mand…®p vapmba yet…® ngwula. Nat n…®mba kat yelav…®ka ndi kat kwunaka woviyaguga al…® ngwula.
\v 14 Lona angwa vat k…®ngiyaa. Avla yelav…®ka woviyaguga l…®ngwa vla nat n…®mba kat wupma yelav…®ka woviyaguga al…® ngwula.
\v 15 Ngwuk mbatna maaawut waalana maawut klalaa nat n…®mba kat kavle yivak kat wana yelav…®t…®ngweya. Wan vapmba awat sowat yet…®ngweyan ngwuk aywaa kavle yigiyangwuk.
\s1 GODNA WAAGANA VATNO TAMBA MAAWUTNA VATNO
\p 
\v 16 Wun kupma ngwuk kat mbut…®gowun. Godna waagan waiga nyaang…®tmba yet…® ngwula. Tamba yelav…®ka yet…®ngwa maawutmba kavle vat ke yet…®ngwa.
\v 17-18 Godna waagan waiga vat n…®na tamba yet…®na maawut waiga vat kapma kapma vat mb…®t. Wan vak v…®l…®l…®k awat sowat walea l…®gamb…®t. Mama n…®mba l…®ga vak vla l…®gamb…®t. Ngi kat t…®ga kwo ana yet…®giyan…®n. Wan v…®l…®l…®k vat waiga nyaang…®tmba yet…®ngweyan lo ngwuk kat ana kwutaa v…®ga l…®giyand…®.
\p 
\v 19 N…®n aywaa tambana maawut ta vat v…®ga l…®gan…®n. Nd…®na vak k…®ngiyan. s…®kwuka yamb…®s…®k kwuka yet…®nja vak. Nat n…®mba kat kavle vat yil…®nja vat. S…®mblan wang…®l…®nja vat.
\v 20 Waagan kat kwunat…®nja vat. S…®vu wal…®nja vat. Nat n…®mba kat walea l…®nja vat. Kaawa viyaga ngambul…®nja vat. T…®pmwigwula yil…®nja vat. Nyingi maawut t…®ga yil…®nja vat. Avla nd…®na mbang…® m…®na kwunapmat yelav…®t…®nja vak. Nat n…®mba kat kai wal…®nja vat. N…®n apma n…®mba n…®n ngwuk kavle n…®mba ngwuk waa wal…®nja vat.
\v 21 Nat n…®mbana nda klavat wal…®nja vat. Nat n…®mba kat vatnyal…®nja vat. N…®ma sakwat n…®ma ngu k…®laa tungwengwan yiga kavle vat yil…®nja vat. Ngi vat vapmba tamba maawutmba yet…®l…®ga n…®mba yet…®l…®gandi. Tak ngwuk kat wan vak wana yiga yet…®l…®ngweya wowun ngwukkat. mbambala nat njamba waigowun. Ngwuk kat. Wan vak ke yiga. Ngi vat kavle vapmba yet…®l…®ga n…®mba God v…®ga l…®ga kavat ana wuleigiyandi.
\p 
\v 22 Godna waagan waiga vat kapma vatna. Nd…®nai waa vapmba yet…®giyaa n…®mba ngi vapmba yet…®giyandi. Nat n…®mba kat woviyaguga l…®giyandi. Ndi solat s…®ga yet…®giyandi. Ndina maawut apma vat t…®nd…®, yet…®giyandi. Ndi kat yinjeya kavle vak kat t…®ga ndina maawutmba k…®mbut ana kwiyatapman yigiyandi. Nat n…®mba kat apma vat yigiyandi. Ndi apma vat t…®ga n…®mbat t…®giyandi. Ndi ngambul…®nja vapmba yet…®l…®gandi.
\v 23 Nat n…®mba kat yelav…®ka yet…®l…®gandi. Ndina maawut waiga kavle vak kat kwulat…®gandi. Ngi vapmba yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat lo ana ndi kat kai wal…®gand…®.
\v 24 Kraist Jisasna mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba tamba yet…®nja ndina kavle maawuk kat kai waga kwagalan…®n. Wan tamba maawut Kraist kiya vla kiyand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga wan tambana maawut wal…®ga vak kat ana wut…®gan…®n. Tamba kiyand…®.
\p 
\v 25 Godna waagan yet…®neya kupi vat n…®n kat kwind…®. Ngi kat t…®ga ndf…®nai waiga vapmba yet…® ngwula.
\v 26 N…®n apma n…®mban…®n. nat n…®mba kavle n…®mba ndi waa wana yelav…®t…®gweya. Nat n…®mbana maawuk kat kavle vat ke yingwa. Nat n…®mba kat t…®pmwigwula ke yingwa.
\c 6
\s1 AWAT SOWAT KWUNAK NGWULA
\p 
\v 1 Wuna k…®ta mbaapma n…®mba, ngwula k…®ta nyan kavle vat yindeyan v…®laa nd…®na maawuk kat kwunak ngwula. Ngwuk Godna waagan wal…®ga nyaang…®tmba yet…®ga n…®mba ngwuk nd…®na maawuk kat kwunak ngwula. Yigumba kwunak ngwula. Ngwulo ngwukkat yigumba v…®ga l…®giyangwuk. Seten ngwuk kat kavle maawut kwiland…®.
\v 2 Awat sowat yelav…®ka kwunak ngwula. Awat sowat kwunakngweyan Kraist waa nyaang…®tmba yet…®ga n…®mba vla l…®giyangwuk.
