\v 11 Tat wawa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wuta nyanamba pensil klalaa wan ng…®ni nyaang…®t wuna taambamba p…®l…®wut…®wun. Wan n…®ma n…®man p…®l…®wukwa vand…® v…®ga l…®gangwuk.
\v 12 Wundi nyangu ngwutna mbang…® p…®pmat t…®ga nyangu. Alagumba la vak kat m…®na yela…®ka l…®ndi. Ndina s…® avla kwusovak wan vak yil…®gandi. Wan n…®mba kupma yelav…®tandi. Juda ndi Jisas Kraist kiya vak kat yelav…®t…®na vak kat mbak v…®landi waa yelav…®tndi. Juda yelav…®tina vak kat v…®laamba n…®n kat n…®ma vat yigiyandi waa yelav…®tndi. Ngi kat t…®ga Juda yet…®la vapmba yet…®l…®gandi.
